<p><strong><em>BerBible</em></strong> is simplified Bible study freeware that includes
the complete <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/English_Standard_Version">ESV</a>
(English Standard Version &copy;2001 from Good News and Crossway Publishers),
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_American_Standard_Bible">NASB</a>
(New American Standard Bible &copy;1995 from The Lockman Foundation),
and the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_King_James_Version">NKJV</a>
(New King James Version &copy;1982 from Thomas Nelson, Inc.) Bibles at no cost.
The learning curve is all but trivial because only the most used functions are implemented:</p>
<ul><li>lookup a specific verse (such as John 3:16)</li>
    <li><a href="faq_searching.php">find</a> verses with one or more word (<i>super-concordance</i>)</li>
</ul>

<p>Word/phrase searching is extremely fast, intuitive,
and very flexible to find what you are looking for.
On most computers, BerBible is running immediately after you <i>launch</i> it, and
searching is faster than you can type.</p>

<p>The small, self-contained 1.9 meg
<i><a href="http://www.berbible.org/download/BerBibleEsvWinStarterKitSetup.exe">ESV Starter Kit</a></i>,
<i><a href="http://www.berbible.org/download/BerBibleNasbWinStarterKitSetup.exe">NASB Starter Kit</a></i>,
and <i><a href="http://www.berbible.org/download/BerBibleNkjvWinStarterKitSetup.exe">NKJV Starter Kit</a></i>
downloads for Windows desktop PC's include the program, the specific Bible itself,
and extensive help and documentation.
See the <a href="http://www.berbible.org/downloads.php">downloads</a> page for other Bible translations,
such as the <a href="http://www.berbible.org/download/BerBibleKjvWinStarterKitSetup.exe">KJV</a>
and a 'bundle' with the <a href="http://www.berbible.org/download/BbEsvNasbNkjvSetup.exe">ESV, NASB, and NKJV</a>.
Versions are available for the <a href="http://www.berbible.org/download/BerBibleEsvPpcStarterKitSetup.exe">Pocket-PC</a> and for
<a href="http://www.berbible.org/download/BerBibleEsvPalmStarterKitSetup.exe">Palm pda's and Treo's</a>.
</p>

<ul><li><span onmouseover="showExtra(miniTutorialExtra)"
    onmouseout="hideExtra(miniTutorialExtra)">
    <span id="mini-tutorial"><u>mini-tutorial</u></span></span> with 7 steps
